========================
Project Task Categories
========================

This module extends the functionality of Project to add main Category field
required on the Task with support filter and group by.

Bug Tracker
===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues <https://github.com/OCA/project/issues>`_.
In case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.
If you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing detailed and welcomed feedback.

